definition: commodities (goods or services) sold to a foreign country, cause to spread in another part of the world
details:
noun
- commodities (goods or services) sold to a foreign country
= synonyms: exportation
verb
- cause to spread in another part of the world
= example: cause to spread in another part of the world
- transfer (electronic data) out of a database or document in a format that can be used by other programs
- sell or transfer abroad
= example: sell or transfer abroad
